The Telegraph - Calcutta : Business
 Wednesday, September 18, 2002 				 I-T raids on Emami offices 
																								Calcutta, Sept. 17 (PTI): The income tax department today carried out search and seizure operations at the offices and production facilities of Emami Ltd. 																								Confirming the nation-wide operations, an I-T department official said that the raids which started on Monday were continuing today, but declined to disclose the value of the seizures.																								Reports said I-T sleuths carried out the operation at nearly 30 Emami offices and production facilities at Calcutta, Chennai, Pondicherry and Balasore. 
